<Install$Dir>.HardDisc4
!Boot,Apps,Printing,Utilities
@.arcs.arc

---
The above parameters are:

<verbose>                  ; 0 or 1
<min buffer size>          ; kbytes, at least size of largest object to be archived
<arc chunk1> <arc chunk 2> ; kbytes, chunk1 for first floppy, chunk2 for 2nd onwards
<source root dir>          ; directory for tree to be archived
<components list>          ; top-level items in tree to be archived (* means all)
<arc root name>            ; root name for arc chunks (postfixed with 01,02..)
